OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy with some patchy light rain
OL,7,Fabout, most of this during the evening
OL,8,Fand from Lough Neagh westwards.
OL,9,FSoutherly winds easing light overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FTemperatures down from
OL,12,FTuesday. A rather cloudy morning with
OL,13,Fa little light patchy rain, then
OL,14,Fmostly dry for the afternoon with
OL,15,Fbrighter spells developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
