OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fearly Thursday, clearing to showers
OL,7,Ffor the afternoon. Friday turning wet
OL,8,Fand windy with best of shelter in
OL,9,Feast. Showers Saturday, more frequent
OL,10,Fin west.
